                technologies: "Appium, Postman, Confluence, Swift/Kotlin (understanding)",
                role: "Mobile QA Specialist & IT Business Analyst",
                achievements: "Ensured secure biometric login, facilitated smooth feature rollout, achieved high user satisfaction.",
                image: "https://placehold.co/800x500/374151/d1d5db?text=Mobile+App+Detail"
            },
            project3: {
                title: "CRM System Upgrade & Integration",
                description: "This project focused on upgrading a legacy CRM system to a modern cloud-based solution and integrating it with various marketing and sales tools. My BA role involved mapping existing processes to the new system and defining integration requirements. As a Tester, I validated data migration accuracy and ensured seamless functionality across integrated modules. The project resulted in a 30% efficiency gain for sales teams.",
                technologies: "Salesforce, MuleSoft, Jira, SQL Server, Excel",
                role: "Business Analyst & Integration Tester",
                achievements: "Improved sales team efficiency by 30%, ensured data integrity during migration, seamless system integration.",
                image: "https://placehold.co/800x500/374151/d1d5db?text=CRM+System+Detail"
            },
            project4: {
                title: "Data Analytics Dashboard Development",
                description: "I collaborated with data scientists and developers to create an interactive data analytics dashboard for executive decision-making. My BA duties included defining key performance indicators (KPIs) and visualization requirements. As a Tester, I validated data accuracy, dashboard performance, and user experience. The dashboard provided critical insights, leading to data-driven strategic decisions.",
